Don't do drugs. 

Author'sNote:

close


On a personal note, the heroin epidemic is something that has affected me most of my adult life. While I myself have never had a use issue– my wife, several ex's, and many close friends have struggled with and died from heroin addiction. The issue is a complex one with many causes and contributing factors some of these factors I wished to highlight in this piece. This is meant to be more than , which frequently only makes things worse– especially for addicts in need of help not punishment. Anyway, that's all I really have to say, and seriously, don't do drugs.







